/MTX    ;Mensajes

;------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/OTX    ;Object Texts
/0 "Una linterna.(encendida)"
;------------------------------------------------------------------------------
/LTX    ;Location Texts
/0 "BASE DE DATOS VACIA - DAAD V2."
